    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Children 4 to 7 years of age

          -  Healthy

          -  English-speaking parent/guardian -

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any underlying condition which would predispose them to the development of sinusitis
